        {
          "angle": 0,
          "height": 146,
          "symHeight": 14.71428571428571,
          "symWidth": 11.45005783689994,
          "text": "IT'S  JUST A  CRAPPY  FLOWER DEITY  TITLE ,  WHAT'S  THE BIG  DEAL ?  FOLLOWING  ME AS  YOUR  MASTER ,  WOULD I  EVER  LET  YOU  GO WITHOUT ?",
          "translation": "إنه مجرد لقب عابر لإلهة الزهور، ما الكبير في ذلك؟ مع كوني سيدتك، هل سأتركك تخسرين؟",
          "width": 240,
          "x": 99,
          "y": 2256
        }
      ],
      "imgHeight": 2939,
      "imgWidth": 700,
      "sourceLanguage": "en",
      "targetLanguage": "ar",
